Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the most fun I've ever had.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo finished the hole at one under.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The winner will be determined{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the results{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of the last group.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubura. Hinoki. Ema.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll need to make it in two strokes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but finishing in even three{\i0}\N{\i1}will be difficult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Missing the par means{\i0}\N{\i1}losing my spot at the playoffs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to go through the grove{\i0}\N{\i1}and land on the 18th fairway,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or bring it to the right side{\i0}\N{\i1}of the fairway of the fifth hole.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If not that…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to hook it onto the green{\i0}\N{\i1}just like Tonbo did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll aim for the final hole.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can it really turn that far?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go! Get there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's going for a two-on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind blew it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This will make it hard to get par.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo used her secret weapon{\i0}\N{\i1}at the final moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As for Tsubura,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she hit a shot completely different from{\i0}\N{\i1}her secret weapon at the last moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why couldn't you get{\i0}\N{\i1}that great one pattern, Tsubura?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm hanging on by a thread.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can just finish in two strokes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to take relief from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The nearest point of relief is…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The green is blocked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But from here, I can see the pin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll go low through the trees,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and roll it to the green.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a bunker in front.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can't carry it to the green,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't land it next to the pin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is the end?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I go through there,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can carry it to the pin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let the ball hop{\i0}\N{\i1}like it usually does.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to hit it high,{\i0}\N{\i1}starting with my swing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To do that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to put{\i0}\N{\i1}all my weight on my left leg.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven-iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll take the eight-iron please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What about relief?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm going to hit from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to hit it off the asphalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not taking the relief?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to loft it as high as possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't enough. I need more!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's only momentary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've put up with this pain for ten years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a little more...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just one more swing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball dropped straight down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not just technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She put her heart and soul into that shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Using the soul as your trump card.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is why I love competitive golf!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's got a chance for birdie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This means…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ema can still win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can get it in…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can catch up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The head of Ema's putter snapped clean off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like a sign from the god of golf...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Golf never goes as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It never goes the way you want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It tests you to your core.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it'd be better to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Life would be so much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just can't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The last ten years were for this shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes it all worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can make a shot like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm not sure when that may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is keep playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to accept things the way they are
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep swinging.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never hit a ball like that before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She put so much into that shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just one shot carries so much weight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of my shots seem to be weightless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! She's close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ema's. If she gets it in\Nshe'll be tied with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a bit left of the pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ride that left wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still close enough to putt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lose if it goes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ema Kurisu gets the birdie putt,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll tie the top spot at one under.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If Tsubura Adaniya can\Nsink it in one putt,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll keep her top spot at one under.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hinoki Otoha can sink it in one putt,\Nshe'll win at two under.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If she misses she'll be at one under.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A play-off against Tonbo Oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean these four\Nhave their own play-off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The conditions are just right\Nfor easily stopping the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she going to chip it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s making sure the ball won't bounce\Noff the pin and roll away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants the ball to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If the ball is spinning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it would bounce right off\Nif it were to hit the pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what she's thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that means she's planning on\Ncarrying the ball right to the pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I swung too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If she hadn't taken it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it really would have hit the pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew it would stop within two steps\Non the first or second bounce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She's relying on the putt now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That was her play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not only the approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's thinking about how\Nto keep par with her next putt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even in this crucial moment,{\i0}\N{\i1}she's able to think clearly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubura is a fearsome competitor, indeed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the exact same distance and line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll both finish the hole{\i0}\N{\i1}at one under if we get it in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person who hits second{\i0}\N{\i1}will have a big advantage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the first player makes the shot,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the second player's line will be exposed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can keep it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Tsubura,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,she's clearly going for the chip-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If she wants to get it in the cup,\Nshe'll have to use a wedge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However, under pressure like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll want her putter as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If she takes her wedge,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a sign that she's well prepared\Nand is incredibly confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect great things from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki practices hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She puts in more time than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how strict\Nher father's coaching may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,she never gives up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And when things go well…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hinoki's father has drilled golf into her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But is that really all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I saw her smiling back then,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew a bright future awaited her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to train her more myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've practiced an approach{\i0}\N{\i1}from this distance thousands of times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, even more than that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now it all comes down to this shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ema taught me so much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As did Tsubura, and Tonbo too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to be a golfer just like them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to fight{\i0}\N{\i1}for everything I've worked for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I did it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used everything I've learned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hinoki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was great.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You showed us how confident you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was an incredible putt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to see what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This could come down\Nto a cut-throat final shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm marking my ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still have a chance to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm a hair farther back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is because{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was Ema's fault that{\i0}\N{\i1}Tsubura missed her tee shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now she's making up for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Which club will she use?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Her putter is broken, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Her putter broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So what will Ema do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll just have to use\None of her other clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A wedge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are two cups.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's on the same line I shot from.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't make it in at the very end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same line as me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Go right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes! It's turning!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More! More!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This puts Ema out of the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ema.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I did my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ball went off course{\i0}\N{\i1}during Ema's wedge putt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I trust this line?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or should I find a new line completely?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the ball had stayed on track,{\i0}\N{\i1}she could have used that line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it may have made{\i0}\N{\i1}things even tougher for her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thinking before a shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The most important part of golf.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But also the most difficult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not as bad as it looks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just stay slightly inside Ema's line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just slightly inside the line!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she hit it too hard?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,G{\i1}o!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She missed the comeback.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:16:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If she gets it in, it'll be\Na playoff against Tonbo Oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make that shot\Nwith your eyes closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Otoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's the playoffs Hinoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, on the fifth hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My ball moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't report it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I kept playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I continued on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to be like Tonbo, Ema, and Tsubura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to play like them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...be disqualified!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That means…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Igaiga? Your face is scary.\N-You… you…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary? Or should I say weird?\N-You…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You… You…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You won, Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Gon! Grandpa Gon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She won the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She really did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tsubura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This hurts! It really hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really a monster after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't win the Japan Woman's Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner at the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,will be the real number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the Japan Woman's Open?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the tournament that decides\Nthe best amateur golfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe we lost to this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about Hinoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hinoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She just went out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to win, not to cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Igaiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I experienced terrible lows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never stole from anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What you've done is theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You stole a single golf stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who cornered and pressured you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to the point that you considered stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to all that pressure,\NI couldn't teach you anything important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I weakened your spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not be able\Nto play golf for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll likely be suspended from competing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By stealing one stroke,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I betrayed Tonbo and the other players.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I deserve the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've learned your lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your heart was hurting\Nas you continued to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you wanted to go back\Nas soon as the ball moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you confessed\Nto everyone on the last hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That must have taken a lot of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Hinoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As a golfer,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,what Hinoki did was truly dishonest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't keep her from\Nhaving a second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue to support her.\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that golf is a game for\Nladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that may not be accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, it is the kind of game that\Ncreates ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the truth of the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No one enters the course initially\Nas a dignified person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I belive they become dignified only\Nby finishing a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nakase…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to quit, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:21:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to come home so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got quite\Nthe souvenir to bring back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will be welcoming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Igaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:22:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I play golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really, really
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,glad I play golf!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your story is only just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're going to get{\i0}\N{\i1}bigger and stronger, Tonbo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love golf!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hooray!{\i0}
